Description:
    Generates add_index migration for selected pg_search scope

    associated_against & trigram not supported

    more info https://github.com/Casecommons/pg_search/wiki/Building-indexes

Example:
    rails generate folio:pg_search_index_migration SomeClass scope_name

    This will create:
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXXXXXXXX_add_scope_name_index_to_some_class_table_name.rb
